{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_02_03",
  "title": "Episode 2 Part 3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "動画とはいえ、{user}さんが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though it's just a video‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "目の前におると思うと、めっちゃ恥ずかしいわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it’s super embarrassing thinking that {user}-san’s right in front of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あんま見やんといて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t look at me too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなじっと見られたら、うち困ります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you keep staring at me like that‚ I’ll be troubled…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふふ、冗談はこれくらいにして本題に入らなな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I should stop joking around and get to the main point.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9333337784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うちだけ尺が延びたら怒られてまうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If only my part is long‚ I’ll get scolded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4333337784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん、いつもホンマにおおきに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ thank you so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9333341599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うち知ってるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1666674932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんなのために沢山営業かけて、スケジュール組んで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re running around doing a lot of business for everyone‚ arranging schedules‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2000008266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "時にはよそで嫌なこと言われても頭下げて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and sometimes even lowering your head and taking abuse from others――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1666674932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも事務所ではしんどい顔いっこも見せへん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but you never show any signs of hardship at the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0333400091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、かっこ良過ぎますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you’re too cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8000066758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんな{user}さんに大事にしてもらえて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're truly blessed to be cherished",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3666707993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "うちらはホンマ幸せもんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "by someone like you‚ {user}-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7000041326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんなおる前やと恥ずかしくて、なかなか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s embarrassing to say it in front of everyone‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8000026067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "言われへんから、この機会に伝えさせてもらいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I’ll take this opportunity to tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9666692734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふ……これ以上語ったらうちが泣けてまうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… I should stop here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5666692734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "これくらいにしとかなな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "before I start crying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3666692734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_yu-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ほなほな～やで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bye bye‚ then!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6666692734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん、こんにちは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ hello.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.881078577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "天動瑠依です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Rui Tendo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.481078577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "初めは優とすみれに手伝ってもらおうと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ I was thinking of having Yu and Sumire help me out‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0335954665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "思ったんですけど、今回は一人で頑張ろうと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but this time I’m going to do my best on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4477452437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さんに伝えたいことは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are a lot of things I want to tell you‚ {user}-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8345244089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "沢山あるんですけど、改めてカメラを前にすると――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but once I’m in front of the camera again――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7810779411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんだか恥ずかしいですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it’s kind of embarrassing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0821889559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着いて、用意した台本通りに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down‚ and just follow the script…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3810780683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まずは、いつもトリエルをマネジメントしていただき",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ thank you very much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.449059677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "本当にありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for always managing TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3810780683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さんに出会わなければ、今の",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I hadn’t met {user}-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9412888209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルはあり得なかった訳ですし感謝しかありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the current TRINITYAiLE wouldn’t exist. I’m filled with nothing but gratitude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5810848076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あとはそうですね。{user}さんから見て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ well. From your perspective‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8211527188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……私って、どうでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…what do you think of me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.014418141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あっ！　どうっていうのはその、変な意味ではなくて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! I don’t mean that in a weird way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.181493473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんアイドルとしてどうか、というお話です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I’m asking what you think of me as an idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1810850619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "意外とそういう真に迫ったお話を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s surprising that we’ve never",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.0354842503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "したことがないなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "had such a serious conversation before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4144183952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こ、今度、ぜひ聞かせて下さいね。私がスケジュールを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ please let me know sometime!",
        "id": ""
      },
