    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_rui-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "押さえておきますから！　それでは、失礼します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll keep my schedule open! Well then‚ excuse me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0810850619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3848883151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEの奥山すみれです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m Sumire Okuyama from TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2515549818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今日は{user}さんに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I’m going to tell you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.2515549818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "沢山『ありがとう』を伝えようと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“thank you” a bunch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.0515549818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さんは、毎日夜遅くまで事務所で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though {user}-san works at the office late every night‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1515549818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事してるのに東京駅まで送り迎えしてくれたり――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you still pick me up and drop me off at Tokyo Station――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9848883151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "学校の宿題の相談にも乗ってくれたり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and you even help me with my school homework‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6182216484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "いつも見守ってくれて、とっても感謝してます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so grateful that you’re always watching over me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.8182216484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それに、もう一度演技のお仕事にチャレンジ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And when I decided to challenge myself with acting again‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.7515549818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "する時なんて、優しく背中を押してくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you gently gave me a push…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9848883151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "共演者さんのことや自分の演技に不安になっても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when I was anxious about my co-stars and my acting‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.3515549818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "一番近くで応援してくれましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you were by my side to cheer me on‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.7182216484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私、すっごくすっごく嬉しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was so‚ so happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.1515549818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが応援してくれると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When {user}-san cheers me on…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.1515549818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "心がじんわりーって温かくなるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "my heart feels all warm and fuzzy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.8182168166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "実家のおこた以上の温もりです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s warmer than the kotatsu at my parents’ house!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.7515501499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ、あと、久しぶりに頭ぽんぽんもしてもらえて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ and when you patted my head after a long time‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.6182157993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_smr-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちがスーって落ち着きました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it made me feel so calm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.984882466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
